		       <TELL "You have no source of fire." CR>
		       <RTRUE>)>)>
	 <COND (<NOT <PRSI? ,MATCH>>
		<TELL ,YOU-CANT "burn something with" AR ,PRSI>)
	       (<NOT <FSET? ,MATCH ,ONBIT>>
		<TELL "It's not lit." CR>)
